<p>Thank you for contacting DJ Misha! Your message was sent successfully and you'll be hearing back shortly.</p>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading">What's Next?</h2>

<p>DJ Misha responds to booking inquiries by text message – usually within a few minutes or when he next checks his phone.</p>

<p>You'll receive a text message soon with a reply and availability information. We may ask a few additional questions about your event to coordinate booking details – this helps us get DJ Misha booked for your event quickly and efficiently.</p>

<p>Once you're ready to confirm your booking, a deposit of 50% of the total balance is required to secure your date. We primarily use Venmo for payments, though additional payment options are available if needed.</p>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Get to Know DJ Misha</h2>

<p>We recommend reading reviews on DJ Misha's <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=dj+misha#lrd=0x80dbffcb31404e13:0x3fae10d8742ab418,1,,," target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Profile page</a> to get a feel for his services and hear from recent satisfied clients.</p>

<p>You can learn more about:</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="/about/">DJ Misha on the About page</a></li>
<li>His music selection process and view actual event playlists on the <a href="/music/">Music page</a></li>
<li>Specific event types like <a href="/services/corporate-event-dj-in-san-diego/">corporate events</a>, <a href="/services/wedding-dj-in-san-diego/">weddings</a>, <a href="/services/party-birthday-dj-in-san-diego/">private parties</a>, and <a href="/dj-saxophone/">DJ and Saxophone</a> performances</li>
</ul>

<p>Be sure to check out the page relevant to your event type for detailed information about what to expect.</p>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Planning a Wedding?</h2>

<p>If you're planning a wedding, don't miss our extensive <a href="/services/wedding-dj-in-san-diego/">wedding planning guide</a>. It covers:</p>

<ul>
<li>Commonly asked questions about the wedding planning process</li>
<li>How we collaborate with you and other vendors</li>
<li>Music and songs request curation</li>
<li>Important timeline details</li>
<li>Coordination with wedding planners</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Follow DJ Misha on Social Media</h2>

<p>Stay connected and get inspired! Follow DJ Misha on <a href="https://www.instagram.com/djmishasd/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a> to:</p>

<ul>
<li>Get a behind-the-scenes peek at amazing parties</li>
<li>Discover playlists from recent events</li>
<li>Read authentic reviews and testimonials from satisfied clients</li>
<li>Stay updated on DJ Misha's latest events and music selections</li>
</ul>

<p>Thank you for getting in touch – we look forward to being part of your special event!</p>

